Tauri externalBin source directory.

The Recall SDK sidecar launcher `recall-desktop-sdk-<target-triple>.exe`
(referenced by `bundle.externalBin` in ../tauri.conf.json) is produced here by
`../../sidecar/recall-sdk-bridge/build.mjs` — a Node Single Executable
Application (SEA) launcher, ~80 MB. It is a build artifact: gitignored
(`src-tauri/binaries/*.exe`) and rebuilt on every `tauri build` via
tauri.conf.json `beforeBuildCommand`. Do not commit it.

See docs/RELEASE.md → "Recall SDK sidecar packaging".
